# All Things Gwinnett — Cursor Rules

## Project Overview
All Things Gwinnett (ATG) is a hyperlocal media brand for Gwinnett County, Georgia.
Stack: Next.js 14 (App Router) + Tailwind CSS + Sanity CMS + Vercel
Live site: allthingsgwinnett.com

---

## Brand Identity

### Aesthetic
Neo-brutalist. Zine-inspired. Think Thrillist meets a local newspaper.
- Hard edges everywhere. No border radius on any interactive element.
- Offset box shadows only (never drop shadows): `box-shadow: 5px 5px 0 #111`
- No gradients. No blur. No rounded corners.
- Dense, editorial layout. Every pixel earns its place.

### Color Palette
```
--paper:     #F4EFE4  /* page background */
--ink:       #111111  /* text, borders, nav bg */
--yellow:    #F2E93E  /* ticker, newsletter, active states, pin mark */
--orange:    #FF6B35  /* primary accent, CTAs, "Gwinnett" in wordmark */
--dk-orange: #7A2800  /* shadows on dark/colored surfaces only */
--card:      #EDEADF  /* hover states, secondary surface */
--mid:       #2A2A2A  /* dark gray subbars */
```

Never use: purple, blue, rounded corners, gradients, generic grays.
Shadow color rule: `#111` on light surfaces, `#7A2800` on dark/orange surfaces.

### Typography
```
font-archivo  → Archivo Black    → display, hero headlines, nav wordmark
font-space    → Space Grotesk 700 → article headlines, card headlines
font-georgia  → Georgia (serif)   → body copy, decks, reviews
font-inter    → Inter 500/700     → UI, navigation, metadata, buttons
```

Google Fonts import:
`https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Archivo+Black&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap`

### Tailwind Brand Tokens
These are already configured in `tailwind.config.js`:
```js
colors: { paper, ink, yellow, orange, 'dk-orange', card, mid }
fontFamily: { archivo, space, inter, georgia }
boxShadow: { brutalist, 'brutalist-sm', 'brutalist-dk', 'brutalist-dk-sm' }
animation: { ticker: '28s linear infinite' }
```

