## Layout System

### Full-Bleed Pattern (CRITICAL)
Every section uses full-bleed background with contained inner content.
ALWAYS use this pattern — never put max-width on the page wrapper:

```tsx
/* Full-bleed color bar — stretches edge to edge */
<div className="bg-ink border-b-2 border-ink w-full">
  {/* Contained content — centered, max 1200px, with gutters */}
  <div className="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6">
    {/* content */}
  </div>
</div>
```

The `<main>` tag always has `className="w-full"` — never `max-w-*` on main.

### Spacing
- Section padding: `py-6` or `py-8` for most sections
- Inner gutters: `px-6` on all inner containers
- Column gaps: `gap-6` or `gap-8`
- Card padding: `p-6` (24px all sides)

