## Component Patterns

### Buttons & CTAs
NEVER use `<button>` elements — browser defaults override styles.
Always use `<span>` or `<a>` with inline styles or Tailwind:

```tsx
<span className="inline-block bg-orange text-white font-inter text-[11px] font-bold
                 uppercase tracking-[1px] px-6 py-3 border-2 border-ink
                 shadow-brutalist-sm cursor-pointer
                 hover:translate-x-[2px] hover:translate-y-[2px] hover:shadow-none
                 transition-all">
  Read the story →
</span>
```

### Category Pills
```tsx
/* Inactive */
<span className="inline-block font-inter text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.8px]
                 px-[14px] py-[8px] border-2 border-ink bg-paper text-ink
                 leading-none cursor-pointer">
  Food & drink
</span>

/* Active */
<span className="inline-block font-inter text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.8px]
                 px-[14px] py-[8px] border-2 border-ink bg-ink text-yellow
                 leading-none cursor-pointer">
  Everything
</span>
```

### Story Tags (color by category)
```tsx
const tagColors = {
  orange:  'bg-orange text-white',          // Food & drink
  yellow:  'bg-yellow text-ink',            // Roads & traffic
  ink:     'bg-ink text-paper',             // Business
  mid:     'bg-mid text-yellow',            // Development
  outline: 'border-2 border-ink text-ink',  // Community/default
}
```

### Nav
- Black background, 50px height
- Logo: ATG pin SVG + "All Things Gwinnett" wordmark ("Gwinnett" in orange)
- Links: 10px, font-inter, semibold, uppercase, gray (#777), yellow on hover
- Newsletter: orange inline button, no dividers between links
- Subtle 1px separator between logo and nav links

### ATG Logo Pin
Single SVG polygon — never composite HTML elements:
```tsx
<svg width="24" viewBox="-7 -7 78 98" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <polygon fill="#7A2800" points="0,0 64,0 64,52 42,52 32,80 22,52 0,52" transform="translate(5,5)"/>
  <polygon fill="#FF6B35" points="0,0 64,0 64,52 42,52 32,80 22,52 0,52"/>
  <text fill="#fff" x="32" y="30" text-anchor="middle" dominant-baseline="middle"
        font-family="'Archivo Black', sans-serif" font-size="22" letter-spacing="-1">ATG</text>
</svg>
