## Common Mistakes to Avoid

1. Never put `max-w-*` on `<main>` — always `w-full`
2. Never use `<button>` — use `<span>` or `<a>` for all clickable elements
3. Never add border-radius to interactive elements
4. Never use drop-shadow — only offset box-shadow
5. Never hardcode colors outside Tailwind tokens
6. Always wrap section content in `max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6`
7. Never use `grid-template-columns` without `minmax(0, 1fr)` to prevent overflow
8. Always use `font-archivo` for display text, never for body text
9. Category pills must be `<span>` not `<button>` to avoid browser style overrides
10. Shadow on dark/orange surfaces must be `#7A2800`, not `#111`

